{"tid":1607600,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武拉曬，就會到和理非","createTime":"2019-10-01T01:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T02:12:49.000Z","uid":74642,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"37a0824cbf6cc54d6c6a7401c3a450bbaa90aac4","tid":1607600,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:53:41.000Z","msg":"我知道身為和理非嘅你會好驚<br />\n今日個風吹到好恒話出面好危險<br />\n但試諗下，如果今日人少，勇武係會一鋪清袋<br />\n<br />\n之後，當勇武比人拉曬，和理非一樣會比人清算<br />\n<br />\n一句講曬<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">不分和勇，十月一，街上見，慶佢老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"01f4eabffee968a8f1109372a10d183410a0251d","tid":1607600,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"十月一，街上見"},{"pid":"538f4d0bdba7037b0663e583d405098655d2e064","tid":1607600,"uid":140492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:54:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十一革命 撥亂反正</span></span>"},{"pid":"f43096537dbcde9c9f1fccbd452bdf8549681d7f","tid":1607600,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:54:14.000Z","msg":"十月一，街上見"},{"pid":"0ea0e0e4be0992f8d4187a46c28f767c17fadf74","tid":1607600,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:54:24.000Z","msg":"十月一，街上見"},{"pid":"f8d57edac0d8413facbdd8838a882e7732dc2fbf","tid":1607600,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:54:34.000Z","msg":"十月一，街上見"},{"pid":"83ad525409ce842f47869024f4a5d8d6f8b19d3d","tid":1607600,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:54:45.000Z","msg":"十月一，街上見"},{"pid":"7bad510dbd317b1721adf8cb542186c58d886f33","tid":1607600,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:54:55.000Z","msg":"十月一，街上見"},{"pid":"85f7795c5fa292ba58dcf333ac055430f5940990","tid":1607600,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"出佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf7d3ae5c12aa96c7044eccfb9fd0e33c1d6292","tid":1607600,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:56:36.000Z","msg":"聽日一戰，睇到呢個手勢就向前衝 打返轉頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1607145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1607145</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"518de8a5ac36221e0a53de4d31aeca6ae50a2e4f","tid":1607600,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55583f191b6e84658d0f5778fb3b72acf691a8a4","tid":1607600,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:06:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六區開花要對準政權，梗係去議員辦事處賀佢老母啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>企起街上面<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>圍警局</strong></span></span>，分區活動就應該<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打游擊戰去搵該區既建制派議員</strong></span></span>同佢地開party一齊賀一賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至於邊一區去邊間就大家自己衡量下喇﹗<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=e46d9a46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n荃灣區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=11a4b272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n沙田區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=97bf428c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=138ffa37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=ea9f691f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=547e98d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"d91fdcc279da7de15dc975e09bae15c844d6bd9c","tid":1607600,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"十月一，街上見"}]}